==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Contline
<hw>Cont"line`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Ropemaking)</fld> <def>The space between the strands on the
outside of a rope.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>The space between the bilges of
two casks stowed side by side.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Contopus</ent>⟦br⟧
